-open:text-token-text-secondary flex aspect-square h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full transition focus-visible:outline-0"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-[22px] w-[22px]"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 21C10.8954 21 10 20.1046 10 19C10 17.8954 10.8954 17 12 17C13.1046 17 14 17.8954 14 19C14 20.1046 13.1046 21 12 21ZM12 14C10.8954 14 10 13.1046 10 12C10 10.8954 10.8954 10 12 10C13.1046 10 14 10.8954 14 12C14 13.1046 13.1046 14 12 14ZM12 7C10.8954 7 10 6.10457 10 5C10 3.89543 10.8954 3 12 3C13.1046 3 14 3.89543 14 5C14 6.10457 13.1046 7 12 7Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></button><button aria-label="Öppna profilmenyn" data-testid="profile-button" class="text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary hover:bg-token-surface-hover radix-state-open:text-token-text-secondary flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full px-1 transition focus-visible:outline-0" type="button" id="radix-«rb0»" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><div class="relative"><div class="relative"><div class="relative flex overflow-hidden rounded-full"><img alt="User" width="32" height="32" class="rounded-xs" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="./marker-icon_files/9a7eef0b1cdc4050403229b5d4444261"></div></div><span class="absolute end-[4.8px] top-[21.5px] -me-2 flex h-3 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-[8px] font-medium text-black" style="width: 1.6rem; box-shadow: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.1) 0px 0px 0px 1.1px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">PLUS</span></div></button></div></div><div class="flex shrink basis-auto flex-col overflow-hidden -mb-(--composer-overlap-px) [--composer-overlap-px:24px] grow"><div class="relative h-full"><div class="flex h-full flex-col overflow-y-auto [scrollbar-gutter:stable]"><div aria-hidden="true" data-edge="true" class="pointer-events-none h-px w-px"></div><div class="@thread-xl/thread:pt-header-height mt-1.5 flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9"><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-1" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="f7fa9340-5fb6-4a00-a455-32236806e84b" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Hej, önskar skapa en webbsida som visar priser för alla publika- och semipublika laddstationer i Sverige. Hur går jag tillväga för att nå dit med minsta möjliga arbete från min sida och hur mycket kan du hjälpa mig med?</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-2" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="01edcaf1-067e-4929-b172-fcf222103cc4" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="244" class="">Hej! Det låter som ett grymt projekt — och jag kan hjälpa dig med nästan <strong data-start="73" data-end="90">allt tekniskt</strong> för att du ska komma igång och slippa så mycket jobb som möjligt själv. Här kommer ett förslag på hur vi når dit med minsta möjliga arbete från din sida:</p>
<hr data-start="246" data-end="249" class="">
<h2 data-start="251" data-end="266" class="">💡 <strong data-start="257" data-end="266">Målet</strong></h2>
<p data-start="267" data-end="384" class="">Visa realtidspriser (eller dagsaktuella) för alla <strong data-start="317" data-end="368">publika och semipublika laddstationer i Sverige</strong> på en webbsida.</p>
<hr data-start="386" data-end="389" class="">
<h2 data-start="391" data-end="418" class="">✅ <strong data-start="396" data-end="418">Steg-för-steg-plan</strong></h2>
<h3 data-start="420" data-end="468" class="">1. <strong data-start="427" data-end="468">Datakälla – Varifrån får vi priserna?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="469" data-end="496" class="">Här finns några alternativ:</p>
<h4 data-start="498" data-end="519" class="">📍 <strong data-start="506" data-end="519">NOBIL API</strong></h4>
<ul data-start="520" data-end="669">
<li data-start="520" data-end="557" class="">
<p data-start="522" data-end="557" class="">Innehåller laddstationer i Sverige.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="558" data-end="622" class="">
<p data-start="560" data-end="622" class="">Innehåller viss metadata, men <strong data-start="590" data-end="621">inte alltid prisinformation</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="623" data-end="669" class="">
<p data-start="625" data-end="669" class="">Dock bra för geodata och grundläggande info.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 data-start="671" data-end="714" class="">🔌 <strong data-start="679" data-end="714">Operatörernas API:er / hemsidor</strong></h4>
<ul data-start="715" data-end="940">
<li data-start="715" data-end="777" class="">
<p data-start="717" data-end="777" class="">Exempel: E.ON, Bee, Mer, Circle K, Vattenfall InCharge m.fl.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="778" data-end="878" class="">
<p data-start="780" data-end="878" class="">Vissa visar priser på sina webbplatser eller via appar – kan eventuellt <strong data-start="852" data-end="863">scrapas</strong> om API saknas.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="879" data-end="940" class="">
<p data-start="881" data-end="940" class="">Vissa har öppna API:er eller erbjuder access vid förfrågan.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 data-start="942" data-end="1002" class="">🧠 <strong data-start="950" data-end="1002">Alternativ: Ladda upp ett statiskt Excel/CSV-ark</strong></h4>
<ul data-start="1003" data-end="1145">
<li data-start="1003" data-end="1145" class="">
<p data-start="1005" data-end="1145" class="">Om du kan få tag på priser från en datakälla (ex. via Excel-rapport från nätägare eller operatör), kan vi visa det på hemsidan utan backend.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1147" data-end="1150" class="">
<h3 data-start="1152" data-end="1186" class="">2. <strong data-start="1159" data-end="1186">Webbsidan – Vad behövs?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1248" class="">Med minsta möjliga arbete från dig kan vi köra detta upplägg:</p>
<div class="group pointer-events-none relative flex justify-center *:pointer-events-auto"><span class="pointer-events-none absolute start-full top-4 z-10 hidden h-full w-fit ps-2 md:block" data-state="closed"><button class="hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary text-token-text-secondary pointer-events-auto rounded-lg px-1 py-1 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></button></span><div class="tableContainer horzScrollShadows relative"><table class="min-w-full" data-start="1250" data-end="1818"><thead data-start="1250" data-end="1321"><tr data-start="1250" data-end="1321"><th data-start="1250" data-end="1269">Komponent</th><th data-start="1269" data-end="1306">Teknikval</th><th data-start="1306" data-end="1321">Beskrivning</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1394" data-end="1818"><tr data-start="1394" data-end="1476"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1394" data-end="1413">Frontend</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1413" data-end="1450">React + Tailwind (eller Next.js)</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1450" data-end="1476">Enkelt, snyggt, snabbt</td></tr><tr data-start="1477" data-end="1564"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1477" data-end="1496">Karta (valfritt)</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1496" data-end="1533">Leaflet / Mapbox / Google Maps</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1533" data-end="1564">Visa laddstationer visuellt</td></tr><tr data-start="1565" data-end="1646"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1565" data-end="1584">Datakälla</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1584" data-end="1621">CSV / JSON / API</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1621" data-end="1646">Laddas in automatiskt</td></tr><tr data-start="1647" data-end="1727"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1647" data-end="1666">Hosting</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1666" data-end="1705">Vercel / Netlify (gratisnivå funkar)</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1705" data-end="1727">Lätt att publicera</td></tr><tr data-start="1728" data-end="1818"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1728" data-end="1747">Uppdatering</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1747" data-end="1784">Cron-jobb via GitHub Actions</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1784" data-end="1818">Automatisk uppdatering av data</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
<hr data-start="1820" data-end="1823" class="">
<h3 data-start="1825" data-end="1863" class="">3. <strong data-start="1832" data-end="1863">Vad kan jag hjälpa dig med?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1864" data-end="1875" class="">Allt detta:</p>
<p data-start="1877" data-end="2103" class="">✅ Sätta upp koden<br data-start="1894" data-end="1897">
✅ Hämta/ladda in data från API eller Excel<br data-start="1939" data-end="1942">
✅ Visualisera laddstationer + priser<br data-start="1978" data-end="1981">
✅ Filtrering (ex. billigast, AC/DC, effekt, operatör)<br data-start="2034" data-end="2037">
✅ Publicera sidan online<br data-start="2061" data-end="2064">
✅ Automatisera uppdatering (om möjligt)</p>
<hr data-start="2105" data-end="2108" class="">
<h2 data-start="2110" data-end="2125" class="">🎯 Ditt jobb</h2>
<p data-start="2126" data-end="2152" class="">Minimalt. Du behöver bara:</p>
<ol data-start="2154" data-end="2355">
<li data-start="2154" data-end="2230" class="">
<p data-start="2157" data-end="2230" class="">Tala om hur du vill att sidan ska se ut (enkel lista? karta? filtrering?)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2231" data-end="2298" class="">
<p data-start="2234" data-end="2298" class="">Hjälpa mig få tillgång till data (API, Excel, manuell inmatning)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2299" data-end="2355" class="">
<p data-start="2302" data-end="2355" class="">Kanske skapa ett GitHub-konto för att kunna publicera</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="2357" data-end="2360" class="">
<p data-start="2362" data-end="2527" class="">Vill du att jag sätter igång direkt med ett exempel i React? Eller vill du börja med en demo som laddar in data från ett Excelark, så kan vi utveckla det vidare sen?</p>
<p data-start="2529" data-end="2604" class="">Berätta hur mycket du vill göra själv och vad du vill jag ska ta hand om 🙌</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-3" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="b5af3188-aba4-4e65-b862-f23da5482dc4" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Mitt Jobb: 1. Utseende ska vara en karta som zoomar in utifrån platsdata och visar vilka laddoperatörer som finns i området samt med en färgkodad punkt, förslagsvis i operatörens egna färger eller opperatörens symbol/varumärke). Detta kompletteras även med en lista brevid som visar aktuella priser. Ska även finnas filtrering för AC/DC, lägsta pris, högst effekt och tillgänglighet (om den datan finns). 2. Hur ska jag hjälpa dig med API. Jag förse dig med API för Nobil. Vilka fler API:er tänker du på? 3. Skapar jag som vanligt ett GitHub-konto och ger dig inloggningsuppgifterna bara eller är det nått mer jag ska tänka på? </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-4" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex items-center"><div class="w-fit" type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-«rb3»" data-state="closed"><div style="width: 1px; height: 1px;"></div></div><div class="inline-block"><button class="my-1 flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold outline-hidden text-token-text-tertiary" type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-«rb4»" data-state="closed"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="mb-[-1px]"><path d="M6 3C4.89543 3 4 3.89543 4 5V13C4 14.1046 4.89543 15 6 15L6 3Z" fill="currentColor"></path><path d="M7 3V15H8.18037L8.4899 13.4523C8.54798 13.1619 8.69071 12.8952 8.90012 12.6858L12.2931 9.29289C12.7644 8.82153 13.3822 8.58583 14 8.58578V3.5C14 3.22386 13.7761 3 13.5 3H7Z" fill="currentColor"></path><path d="M11.3512 15.5297L9.73505 15.8529C9.38519 15.9229 9.07673 15.6144 9.14671 15.2646L9.46993 13.6484C9.48929 13.5517 9.53687 13.4628 9.60667 13.393L12.9996 10C13.5519 9.44771 14.4473 9.44771 14.9996 10C15.5519 10.5523 15.5519 11.4477 14.9996 12L11.6067 15.393C11.5369 15.4628 11.448 15.5103 11.3512 15.5297Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Det sparade minnet har uppdaterats</button></div></div><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="348d90ba-27c0-430a-b315-c8af7ea3b1d2" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="78" class="">Perfekt! Grymt tydligt och genomtänkt. Här är nästa steg baserat på dina svar:</p>
<hr data-start="80" data-end="83" class="">
<h2 data-start="85" data-end="128" class="">✅ <strong data-start="90" data-end="128">1. UI &amp; Funktioner (Din kravlista)</strong></h2>
<p data-start="129" data-end="167" class="">Vi siktar på en karta + sidopanel med:</p>
<ul data-start="169" data-end="505">
<li data-start="169" data-end="306" class="">
<p data-start="171" data-end="202" class="">🗺️ <strong data-start="175" data-end="202">Karta med laddstationer</strong></p>
<ul data-start="205" data-end="306">
<li data-start="205" data-end="214" class="">
<p data-start="207" data-end="214" class="">Zoombar</p>
</li>
<li data-start="217" data-end="256" class="">
<p data-start="219" data-end="256" class="">Färgkodad punkt (baserat på operatör)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="259" data-end="306" class="">
<p data-start="261" data-end="306" class="">Symbol/varumärke per operatör om tillgängligt</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="308" data-end="397" class="">
<p data-start="310" data-end="337" class="">📋 <strong data-start="313" data-end="337">Lista bredvid kartan</strong></p>
<ul data-start="340" data-end="397">
<li data-start="340" data-end="397" class="">
<p data-start="342" data-end="397" class="">Visar priser, operatör, laddtyp, effekt, tillgänglighet</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="399" data-end="505" class="">
<p data-start="401" data-end="424" class="">🔎 <strong data-start="404" data-end="424">Filterfunktioner</strong></p>
<ul data-start="427" data-end="505">
<li data-start="427" data-end="436" class="">
<p data-start="429" data-end="436" class="">AC / DC</p>
</li>
<li data-start="439" data-end="452" class="">
<p data-start="441" data-end="452" class="">Lägsta pris</p>
</li>
<li data-start="455" data-end="470" class="">
<p data-start="457" data-end="470" class="">Högsta effekt</p>
</li>
<li data-start="473" data-end="505" class="">
<p data-start="475" data-end="505" class="">Tillgänglighet (om data finns)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="507" data-end="510" class="">
<h2 data-start="512" data-end="553" class="">🔌 <strong data-start="518" data-end="553">2. API:er – vilka är relevanta?</strong></h2>
<p data-start="554" data-end="674" class="">Du nämner att du fixar tillgång till <strong data-start="591" data-end="604">NOBIL API</strong> – toppen! Det är en bra start, och vi kan bygga en första MVP på det.</p>
<p data-start="676" data-end="761" class="">Men prisinfo finns inte alltid i NOBIL, så för bästa resultat bör vi komplettera med:</p>
<div class="group pointer-events-none relative flex justify-center *:pointer-events-auto"><span class="pointer-events-none absolute start-full top-4 z-10 hidden h-full w-fit ps-2 md:block" data-state="closed"><button class="hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary text-token-text-secondary pointer-events-auto rounded-lg px-1 py-1 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></button></span><div class="tableContainer horzScrollShadows relative"><table class="min-w-full" data-start="763" data-end="1115"><thead data-start="763" data-end="804"><tr data-start="763" data-end="804"><th data-start="763" data-end="774">Operatör</th><th data-start="774" data-end="791">Har öppet API?</th><th data-start="791" data-end="804">Kommentar</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="847" data-end="1115"><tr data-start="847" data-end="920"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="847" data-end="875"><strong data-start="849" data-end="874">InCharge (Vattenfall)</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="875" data-end="879">❌</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="879" data-end="920">Endast via app/hemsida – ev. scraping</td></tr><tr data-start="921" data-end="971"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="921" data-end="938"><strong data-start="923" data-end="937">E.ON Drive</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="938" data-end="942">❌</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="942" data-end="971">Appbaserat – ev. scraping</td></tr><tr data-start="972" data-end="1007"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="972" data-end="982"><strong data-start="974" data-end="981">Mer</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="982" data-end="986">❓</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="986" data-end="1007">Delvis API-access</td></tr><tr data-start="1008" data-end="1061"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1008" data-end="1028"><strong data-start="1010" data-end="1027">Bee (Rejlers)</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1028" data-end="1032">❓</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1032" data-end="1061">Oklart – går att kontakta</td></tr><tr data-start="1062" data-end="1115"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1062" data-end="1091"><strong data-start="1064" data-end="1090">Clever, Circle K, OKQ8</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1091" data-end="1095">❌</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="1095" data-end="1115">Inga publika API</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
<p data-start="1117" data-end="1144" class="">🔧 Jag kan hjälpa till att:</p>
<ul data-start="1145" data-end="1323">
<li data-start="1145" data-end="1187" class="">
<p data-start="1147" data-end="1187" class="">Kontakta operatörer och be om API-access</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1188" data-end="1247" class="">
<p data-start="1190" data-end="1247" class="">Skapa scrapers där det är tillåtet (och tekniskt möjligt)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1248" data-end="1323" class="">
<p data-start="1250" data-end="1323" class="">Designa fallback så att vi alltid visar <em data-start="1290" data-end="1297">någon</em> data även utan exakt pris</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1325" data-end="1328" class="">
<h2 data-start="1330" data-end="1365" class="">🔐 <strong data-start="1336" data-end="1365">3. GitHub – Så här gör du</strong></h2>
<ol data-start="1366" data-end="1668">
<li data-start="1366" data-end="1422" class="">
<p data-start="1369" data-end="1422" class=""><strong data-start="1369" data-end="1395">Skapa ett GitHub-konto</strong> (om du inte redan har ett)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1423" data-end="1471" class="">
<p data-start="1426" data-end="1471" class=""><strong data-start="1426" data-end="1449">Skapa ett nytt repo</strong> t.ex. <code data-start="1456" data-end="1471">laddpriskarta</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1472" data-end="1580" class="">
<p data-start="1475" data-end="1532" class="">Ge mig <strong data-start="1482" data-end="1505">Collaborator-access</strong> (via min GitHub-användare)</p>
<ul data-start="1536" data-end="1580">
<li data-start="1536" data-end="1580" class="">
<p data-start="1538" data-end="1580" class="">Alternativt: skicka ett GitHub invite-länk</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1581" data-end="1668" class="">
<p data-start="1584" data-end="1668" class=""><strong data-start="1584" data-end="1616">Dela API-nycklar (som NOBIL)</strong> via t.ex. mail eller GitHub Secrets (rekommenderas)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1670" data-end="1824" class="">💡 <strong data-start="1673" data-end="1682">Tips:</strong> Du <em data-start="1686" data-end="1700">behöver inte</em> ge mig inlogg. Bara skicka repo-invite som <em data-start="1744" data-end="1758">collaborator</em> (då har jag push-access men inte till dina inloggningsuppgifter).</p>
<hr data-start="1826" data-end="1829" class="">
<h2 data-start="1831" data-end="1847" class="">⏭️ Nästa steg</h2>
<p data-start="1848" data-end="1861" class="">Jag föreslår:</p>
<ol data-start="1863" data-end="2174">
<li data-start="1863" data-end="1952" class="">
<p data-start="1866" data-end="1952" class="">Du skickar mig NOBIL API-nyckeln (via t.ex. GitHub secret eller här om det är bråttom)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1953" data-end="2114" class="">
<p data-start="1956" data-end="1978" class="">Jag sätter upp en MVP:</p>
<ul data-start="1982" data-end="2114">
<li data-start="1982" data-end="1999" class="">
<p data-start="1984" data-end="1999" class="">Karta (Leaflet)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2003" data-end="2025" class="">
<p data-start="2005" data-end="2025" class="">Platsdata från NOBIL</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2029" data-end="2058" class="">
<p data-start="2031" data-end="2058" class="">Färgkodade operatörspunkter</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2062" data-end="2114" class="">
<p data-start="2064" data-end="2114" class="">Enkel lista med grundinfo (namn, operatör, effekt)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="2115" data-end="2174" class="">
<p data-start="2118" data-end="2174" class="">Vi lägger till filtrering, prisdata och symbolik stegvis</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="2176" data-end="2306" class="">Vill du att jag kickar igång koden nu direkt (i React/Next.js), eller ska jag först sätta upp en grunddesign för dig att titta på?</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-5" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="9290f88f-0214-4b73-aa53-30b05df13d11" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Vad bra! Medan jag skapar GitHub konto så får du gärna sålänge sätta upp en grunddesign☺</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-6" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread