"ͼ2d">filter</span><span class="ͼ2f">(</span><span class="ͼ2f">(</span><span class="ͼ2a">s</span><span class="ͼ2f">)</span> <span class="ͼ2f">=&gt;</span> <span class="ͼ2f">{</span></div><div class="cm-line">    <span class="ͼ29">if</span> <span class="ͼ2f">(</span><span class="ͼ2f">!</span><span class="ͼ2a">filterAC</span> <span class="ͼ2f">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="ͼ2a">s</span><span class="ͼ2f">.</span><span class="ͼ2a">type</span> <span class="ͼ2f">===</span> <span class="ͼ2h">"AC"</span><span class="ͼ2f">)</span> <span class="ͼ29">return</span> <span class="ͼ28">false</span><span class="ͼ2f">;</span></div><div class="cm-line">    <span class="ͼ29">if</span> <span class="ͼ2f">(</span><span class="ͼ2f">!</span><span class="ͼ2a">filterDC</span> <span class="ͼ2f">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="ͼ2a">s</span><span class="ͼ2f">.</span><span class="ͼ2a">type</span> <span class="ͼ2f">===</span> <span class="ͼ2h">"DC"</span><span class="ͼ2f">)</span> <span class="ͼ29">return</span> <span class="ͼ28">false</span><span class="ͼ2f">;</span></div><div class="cm-line">    <span class="ͼ29">return</span> <span class="ͼ28">true</span><span class="ͼ2f">;</span></div><div class="cm-line">  <span class="ͼ2f">}</span><span class="ͼ2f">)</span><span class="ͼ2f">;</span></div><div class="cm-line"><br></div><div class="cm-line">  <span class="ͼ29">return</span> <span class="ͼ2f">(</span></div><div class="cm-line">    <span class="ͼ2i">&lt;</span><span class="ͼ28">div</span> <span class="ͼ2a">className</span><span class="ͼ2f">=</span><span class="ͼ2h">"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 h-screen"</span><span class="ͼ2i">&gt;</span></div><div class="cm-line">      <span class="ͼ2i">&lt;</span><span class="ͼ28">div</span> <span class="ͼ2a">className</span><span class="ͼ2f">=</span><span class="ͼ2h">"col-span-2"</span><span class="ͼ2i">&gt;</span></div><div class="cm-line">        <span class="ͼ2i">&lt;</span><span class="ͼ2c">MapContainer</span> <span class="ͼ2a">center</span><span class="ͼ2f">=</span><span class="ͼ2f">{</span><span class="ͼ2f">[</span><span class="ͼ2e">59.3293</span><span class="ͼ2f">,</span> <span class="ͼ2e">18.0686</span><span class="ͼ2f">]</span><span class="ͼ2f">}</span> <span class="ͼ2a">zoom</span><span class="ͼ2f">=</span><span class="ͼ2f">{</span><span class="ͼ2e">6</span><span class="ͼ2f">}</span> <span class="ͼ2a">className</span><span class="ͼ2f">=</span><span class="ͼ2h">"h-full w-full"</span><span class="ͼ2i">&gt;</span></div><div class="cm-line">          <span class="ͼ2i">&lt;</span><span class="ͼ2c">TileLayer</span></div><div class="cm-line">            <span class="ͼ2a">attribution</span><span class="ͼ2f">=</span><span class="ͼ2h">'&amp;copy; OpenStreetMap'</span></div><div class="cm-line">            <span class="ͼ2a">url</span><span class="ͼ2f">=</span><span class="ͼ2h">"https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png"</span></div><div class="cm-line">          <span class="ͼ2i">/&gt;</span></div><div class="cm-line">          <span class="ͼ2f">{</span><span class="ͼ2a">filteredStations</span><span class="ͼ2f">.</span><span class="ͼ2d">map</span><span class="ͼ2f">(</span><span class="ͼ2f">(</span><span class="ͼ2a">station</span><span class="ͼ2f">)</span> <span class="ͼ2f">=&gt;</span> <span class="ͼ2f">(</span></div><div class="cm-line">            <span class="ͼ2i">&lt;</span><span class="ͼ2c">Marker</span></div><div class="cm-line">              <span class="ͼ2a">key</span><span class="ͼ2f">=</span><span class="ͼ2f">{</span><span class="ͼ2a">station</span><span class="ͼ2f">.</span><span class="ͼ2a">id</span><span class="ͼ2f">}</span></div><div class="cm-gap" style="height: 616px;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="pointer-events-none relative flex h-full shrink-0 z-20 basis-0" style="width: 0px; opacity: 1;"><div class="pointer-events-auto absolute start-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-0 overflow-visible"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></main></section></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 z-20 h-24 w-full transition-colors" style="height: 4em; background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));"></div></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="595cdc7f-b6fb-4211-89c4-f5e247b75296" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="77" class="">Toppen! Jag har nu skapat en <strong data-start="29" data-end="52">grunddesign i React</strong> med följande funktioner:</p>
<ul data-start="79" data-end="321">
<li data-start="79" data-end="123" class="">
<p data-start="81" data-end="123" class="">🗺️ Karta (Leaflet) centrerad över Sverige</p>
</li>
<li data-start="124" data-end="152" class="">
<p data-start="126" data-end="152" class="">📋 Lista med laddstationer</p>
</li>
<li data-start="153" data-end="181" class="">
<p data-start="155" data-end="181" class="">✅ Filtrering för AC och DC</p>
</li>
<li data-start="182" data-end="250" class="">
<p data-start="184" data-end="250" class="">🧪 Mockad datainläsning från lokal JSON (ersätts med NOBIL senare)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="251" data-end="321" class="">
<p data-start="253" data-end="321" class="">🔧 Struktur redo för att lägga in operatörsspecifika färger/symboler</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="323" data-end="362" class="">När du har GitHub-kontot redo, kan jag:</p>
<ol data-start="363" data-end="482">
<li data-start="363" data-end="385" class="">
<p data-start="366" data-end="385" class="">Ladda upp projektet</p>
</li>
<li data-start="386" data-end="411" class="">
<p data-start="389" data-end="411" class="">Ansluta till NOBIL API</p>
</li>
<li data-start="412" data-end="482" class="">
<p data-start="415" data-end="482" class="">Bygga vidare med prisfiltrering, tillgänglighet, och operatörslogik</p>
</li>
</ol>
