-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="293be814-6e7d-4656-ae1d-639d1ce3cfdc" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="38" class="">Bra fråga! Här är vad du bör tänka på:</p>
<hr data-start="40" data-end="43" class="">
<h2 data-start="45" data-end="85" class="">👥 <strong data-start="51" data-end="85">Privat eller Public på GitHub?</strong></h2>
<h3 data-start="87" data-end="140" class="">🔓 <strong data-start="94" data-end="140">Public (Rekommenderas i början om möjligt)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="141" data-end="152" class="">✅ Fördelar:</p>
<ul data-start="153" data-end="309">
<li data-start="153" data-end="211" class="">
<p data-start="155" data-end="211" class="">Jag (och andra om du vill) kan se och hjälpa till direkt</p>
</li>
<li data-start="212" data-end="279" class="">
<p data-start="214" data-end="279" class="">Du kan publicera webbplatsen enkelt via GitHub Pages eller Vercel</p>
</li>
<li data-start="280" data-end="309" class="">
<p data-start="282" data-end="309" class="">Gratis i alla GitHub-planer</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="311" data-end="324" class="">🚫 Nackdelar:</p>
<ul data-start="325" data-end="434">
<li data-start="325" data-end="434" class="">
<p data-start="327" data-end="434" class="">Koden är öppen för alla (lägg inte in API-nycklar direkt i koden – vi använder <code data-start="406" data-end="412">.env</code> eller GitHub Secrets)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="436" data-end="439" class="">
<h3 data-start="441" data-end="458" class="">🔒 <strong data-start="448" data-end="458">Privat</strong></h3>
<p data-start="459" data-end="470" class="">✅ Fördelar:</p>
<ul data-start="471" data-end="548">
<li data-start="471" data-end="512" class="">
<p data-start="473" data-end="512" class="">Bara du (och de du bjuder in) ser koden</p>
</li>
<li data-start="513" data-end="548" class="">
<p data-start="515" data-end="548" class="">Bra om du har kommersiella planer</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="550" data-end="563" class="">🚫 Nackdelar:</p>
<ul data-start="564" data-end="673">
<li data-start="564" data-end="614" class="">
<p data-start="566" data-end="614" class="">Kräver manuell inbjudan för mig att kunna hjälpa</p>
</li>
<li data-start="615" data-end="673" class="">
<p data-start="617" data-end="673" class="">Begränsningar i GitHub Pages (kan inte publicera direkt)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="675" data-end="678" class="">
<h2 data-start="680" data-end="703" class="">✨ <strong data-start="685" data-end="703">Rekommendation</strong></h2>
<p data-start="704" data-end="772" class="">Skapa <strong data-start="710" data-end="725">public repo</strong> för nu. Du kan alltid byta till privat senare.</p>
<p data-start="774" data-end="789" class="">När du är klar:</p>
<ol data-start="790" data-end="901">
<li data-start="790" data-end="815" class="">
<p data-start="793" data-end="815" class="">Skicka repo-länken hit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="816" data-end="901" class="">
<p data-start="819" data-end="901" class="">Bjud in mig som <em data-start="835" data-end="849">Collaborator</em> (eller ge GitHub-namnet jag ska skicka invite till)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="903" data-end="911" class="">Redo? 😄</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-11" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="76fc5f37-7206-4eeb-b694-d2663b14f1e6" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Great! Ska jag välja något speciellt under "add gitignore" och "Choose a licence" eller kör jag bara default?</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-12" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="2df7932c-000a-44dd-b7d7-924d03c067ea" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="61" class="">Snyggt! Här är vad du bör välja vid skapande av GitHub-repot:</p>
<hr data-start="63" data-end="66" class="">
<h3 data-start="68" data-end="92" class="">✅ <strong data-start="74" data-end="92">Add .gitignore</strong></h3>
<p data-start="93" data-end="241" class="">Ja, <strong data-start="97" data-end="131">välj ett <code data-start="108" data-end="120">.gitignore</code> för Node</strong> (eller <code data-start="139" data-end="148">Node.js</code>) – eftersom React-projektet kommer ha <code data-start="187" data-end="201">node_modules</code>, byggfiler etc. vi inte vill checka in.</p>
<ul data-start="243" data-end="275">
<li data-start="243" data-end="275" class="">
<p data-start="245" data-end="275" class="">I dropdownen, välj: <strong data-start="265" data-end="275"><code data-start="267" data-end="273">Node</code></strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="277" data-end="280" class="">
<h3 data-start="282" data-end="300" class="">📄 <strong data-start="289" data-end="300">License</strong></h3>
<p data-start="301" data-end="352" class="">Detta är valfritt, men här är lite hjälp att välja:</p>
<div class="group pointer-events-none relative flex justify-center *:pointer-events-auto"><span class="pointer-events-none absolute start-full top-4 z-10 hidden h-full w-fit ps-2 md:block" data-state="closed"><button class="hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary text-token-text-secondary pointer-events-auto rounded-lg px-1 py-1 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></button></span><div class="tableContainer horzScrollShadows relative"><table class="min-w-full" data-start="354" data-end="736"><thead data-start="354" data-end="405"><tr data-start="354" data-end="405"><th data-start="354" data-end="367">Alternativ</th><th data-start="367" data-end="385">Vad det betyder</th><th data-start="385" data-end="405">Rekommenderas om</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="459" data-end="736"><tr data-start="459" data-end="610"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="459" data-end="481"><strong data-start="461" data-end="468">MIT</strong> (vanligast)</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)] min-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)/3)]" data-start="481" data-end="535">Fri användning, modifiering, kommersiell användning</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)] min-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)/3)]" data-start="535" data-end="610">Du vill att andra fritt ska kunna använda, förbättra eller bygga vidare</td></tr><tr data-start="611" data-end="736"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="611" data-end="630"><strong data-start="613" data-end="629">Ingen licens</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)] min-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)/3)]" data-start="630" data-end="683">Då har andra <em data-start="645" data-end="651">inte</em> rätt att kopiera eller använda</td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)] min-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)/3)]" data-start="683" data-end="736">Du är osäker eller vill ha full kontroll i början</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
<p data-start="738" data-end="857" class="">💡 <strong data-start="741" data-end="750">Tips:</strong> Välj <strong data-start="756" data-end="763">MIT</strong> om du är ok med att andra lär sig av eller använder koden. Du kan alltid ändra licens senare.</p>
<hr data-start="859" data-end="862" class="">
<h3 data-start="864" data-end="887" class="">✨ Så: Kör på detta:</h3>
<ul data-start="888" data-end="990">
<li data-start="888" data-end="922" class="">
<p data-start="890" data-end="922" class=""><code data-start="890" data-end="894">✔️</code> Add <code data-start="899" data-end="911">.gitignore</code> – <strong data-start="914" data-end="922">Node</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="923" data-end="990" class="">
<p data-start="925" data-end="990" class=""><code data-start="925" data-end="929">✔️</code> Choose a license – <strong data-start="949" data-end="956">MIT</strong> (eller lämna tom om du är osäker)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="992" data-end="1074" class="">När du är klar, skicka gärna repo-länken här så pushar jag in första versionen! 🚀</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-13" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="e18fbf85-6b74-4168-a4bb-ed846ba1f264" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Great! Hittar ingen knapp för att dela eller bjuda in, men denna länk kanske räcker? https://github.com/Laddpriskollen/laddpriskarta</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-14" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="da64260b-645f-4aa8-aac2-d8d3091b3591" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="76" class="">Perfekt! Tack för länken 🙌<br data-start="27" data-end="30">
Det ser ut som du gjort allt rätt. Nästa steg:</p>
<hr data-start="78" data-end="81" class="">
<h2 data-start="83" data-end="132" class="">✅ <strong data-start="88" data-end="132">Så här bjuder du in mig som Collaborator</strong></h2>
<ol data-start="133" data-end="554">
<li data-start="133" data-end="253" class="">
<p data-start="136" data-end="253" class="">Gå till ditt repo: <a data-start="155" data-end="253" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="" href="https://github.com/Laddpriskollen/laddpriskarta">https://github.com/Laddpriskollen/laddpriskarta</a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="254" data-end="310" class="">
<p data-start="257" data-end="310" class="">Klicka på <strong data-start="267" data-end="279">Settings</strong> (uppe till höger i repo-menyn)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="311" data-end="386" class="">
<p data-start="314" data-end="386" class="">I vänstermenyn, välj <strong data-start="335" data-end="362">Collaborators and teams</strong> eller <strong data-start="369" data-end="386">Manage access</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="387" data-end="425" class="">
<p data-start="390" data-end="425" class="">Klicka på <strong data-start="400" data-end="425">Invite a collaborator</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="426" data-end="533" class="">
<p data-start="429" data-end="533" class="">Ange mitt GitHub-namn (skicka gärna ett alias du vill använda om du vill att jag gör det från mitt håll)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="534" data-end="554" class="">
<p data-start="537" data-end="554" class="">Bekräfta inbjudan</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="556" data-end="559" class="">
<h2 data-start="561" data-end="605" class="">🔄 Alternativ: Du skickar ett invite-länk</h2>
<p data-start="606" data-end="705" class="">När du bjuder in mig, kommer du få en <strong data-start="644" data-end="661">Invite-prompt</strong> som du kan kopiera som länk och skicka hit.</p>
<hr data-start="707" data-end="710" class="">
<p data-start="712" data-end="748" class="">✅ Så fort jag har access kommer jag:</p>
<ul data-start="749" data-end="902">
<li data-start="749" data-end="787" class="">
<p data-start="751" data-end="787" class="">Ladda upp all kod från grunddesignen</p>
</li>
<li data-start="788" data-end="841" class="">
<p data-start="790" data-end="841" class="">Lägga in en mockad <code data-start="809" data-end="829">mock-stations.json</code> i <code data-start="832" data-end="841">/public</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="842" data-end="902" class="">
<p data-start="844" data-end="902" class="">Strukturera projektet för framtida koppling till NOBIL API</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="904" data-end="1019" class="">Vill du att jag pushar med Vite + React + Tailwind som bas? Det blir snabbt och enkelt att deploya t.ex. på Vercel.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-15" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="0885845e-7579-4f49-b799-a00562890758" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">vad är ditt github namn?</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-16" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--th