ative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="266b0d5c-18eb-46d5-8166-d6f285385876" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="81" class="">Bra fråga! Enligt både dokumentationen och hur deras system fungerar i praktiken:</p>
<hr data-start="83" data-end="86" class="">
<h2 data-start="88" data-end="137" class="">🔐 <strong data-start="94" data-end="137">API-nyckel för NOBIL – hur får man den?</strong></h2>
<p data-start="139" data-end="269" class="">Tyvärr går det <strong data-start="154" data-end="179">inte att automatisera</strong> skapandet av en API-nyckel direkt via webblänk (som <code data-start="232" data-end="252">search_apiVer3.php</code>), utan du måste:</p>
<h3 data-start="271" data-end="310" class="">✅ <strong data-start="277" data-end="310">Manuellt ansöka om API-nyckel</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="311" data-end="563">
<li data-start="311" data-end="377" class="">
<p data-start="314" data-end="377" class="">Gå till: <a data-start="323" data-end="377" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="">https://info.nobil.no/api</a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="378" data-end="434" class="">
<p data-start="381" data-end="434" class="">Scrolla ner till formuläret under <em data-start="415" data-end="434">"Request API key"</em></p>
</li>
<li data-start="435" data-end="550" class="">
<p data-start="438" data-end="445" class="">Fyll i:</p>
<ul data-start="449" data-end="550">
<li data-start="449" data-end="474" class="">
<p data-start="451" data-end="474" class="">Kontaktperson / företag</p>
</li>
<li data-start="478" data-end="509" class="">
<p data-start="480" data-end="509" class="">Kort beskrivning av projektet</p>
</li>
<li data-start="513" data-end="550" class="">
<p data-start="515" data-end="550" class="">Hur ofta du planerar att hämta data</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="551" data-end="563" class="">
<p data-start="554" data-end="563" class="">Skicka in</p>
</li>
</ol>
<blockquote data-start="565" data-end="639">
<p data-start="567" data-end="639" class="">🕐 Det brukar ta 1–2 arbetsdagar innan du får din API-nyckel via e-post.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="641" data-end="644" class="">
<h2 data-start="646" data-end="688" class="">🔎 Vad gör länken <code data-start="667" data-end="687">search_apiVer3.php</code>?</h2>
<p data-start="689" data-end="700" class="">Den länken:</p>
<ul data-start="701" data-end="856">
<li data-start="701" data-end="754" class="">
<p data-start="703" data-end="754" class="">Är en <strong data-start="709" data-end="725">API-endpoint</strong> för att söka efter stationer</p>
</li>
<li data-start="755" data-end="813" class="">
<p data-start="757" data-end="813" class=""><strong data-start="757" data-end="813">Fungerar endast om du redan har en giltig API-nyckel</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="814" data-end="856" class="">
<p data-start="816" data-end="856" class="">Kräver <code data-start="823" data-end="842">apiKey=din_nyckel</code> som parameter</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="858" data-end="866" class="">Exempel:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="867" data-end="950"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">ruby</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378 6.10476 20.3159L8.97693 19.8372C9.72813 19.712 10.1037 19.6494 10.4542 19.521C10.7652 19.407 11.0608 19.2549 11.3343 19.068C11.6425 18.8575 11.9118 18.5882 12.4503 18.0497L20 10.5C21.3807 9.11929 21.3807 6.88071 20 5.5C18.6193 4.11929 16.3807 4.11929 15 5.5L7.45026 13.0497C6.91175 13.5882 6.6425 13.8575 6.43197 14.1657C6.24513 14.4392 6.09299 14.7348 5.97903 15.0458C5.85062 15.3963 5.78802 15.7719 5.66282 16.5231Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M14.5 7L18.5 11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>Redigera</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre!"><span><span><span class="hljs-symbol">https:</span></span><span>/</span><span><span class="hljs-regexp">/nobil.no/api</span></span><span><span class="hljs-regexp">/client/search</span></span><span>_apiVer3.php?apikey=</span><span><span class="hljs-variable constant_">DIN_NYCKEL</span></span><span>&amp;country=</span><span><span class="hljs-variable constant_">SE</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="952" data-end="955" class="">
<h2 data-start="957" data-end="978" class="">🎯 Rekommendation:</h2>
<p data-start="979" data-end="1120" class="">Skicka in en ansökan för API-nyckel nu – du behöver bara göra det en gång, och sen kan vi koppla in den direkt i appen med <code data-start="1102" data-end="1111">fetch()</code> i React.</p>
<p data-start="1122" data-end="1244" class="">Vill du ha hjälp att skriva ett bra meddelande i ansökan? Jag kan formulera ett kort och tydligt utkast åt dig om du vill.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-25" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="71ef0e01-6673-4d00-8207-d2e15b228b10" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Ja tack, du får gärna hjälpa mig med det</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-26" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="a6008d35-fbd8-430b-bae0-f5f34dc8943e" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="120" class="">Självklart! Här är ett förslag på ett kort och tydligt meddelande att skicka in till NOBIL när du ansöker om API-nyckel:</p>
<hr data-start="122" data-end="125" class="">
<h3 data-start="127" data-end="181" class="">📩 <strong data-start="134" data-end="181">Förslag – Meddelande till NOBIL vid ansökan</strong></h3>
<blockquote data-start="183" data-end="942">
<p data-start="185" data-end="193" class=""><strong data-start="185" data-end="193">Hej,</strong></p>
<p data-start="198" data-end="368" class="">Jag driver ett projekt där jag bygger en webbsida som visar publika och semipublika laddstationer i Sverige, inklusive information om pris, tillgänglighet och operatör.</p>
<p data-start="373" data-end="507" class="">Syftet är att underlätta för elbilsägare att hitta och jämföra laddstationer på ett enkelt sätt via karta och filtreringsfunktioner.</p>
<p data-start="512" data-end="627" class="">API:t från NOBIL kommer att användas för att hämta geografisk och teknisk information om laddstationer i Sverige.</p>
<p data-start="632" data-end="777" class="">Webbplatsen kommer initialt att vara öppen för allmänheten och ej kommersiell, och jag uppskattar därför möjligheten att få tillgång till API:et.</p>
<p data-start="782" data-end="858" class="">Planerad användning: 1–4 API-anrop per dag för uppdatering av stationdata.</p>
<p data-start="863" data-end="942" class="">Vänliga hälsningar,<br data-start="882" data-end="885">
<em data-start="887" data-end="900">[Ditt namn]</em><br data-start="900" data-end="903">
<em data-start="905" data-end="942">[Ev. företagsnamn/projektwebbplats]</em></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="944" data-end="947" class="">
<p data-start="949" data-end="1107" class="">Du kan förstås anpassa den efter din egen stil – men detta är en bra, tydlig start. När du fått nyckeln, så hjälper jag dig att lägga in den säkert i koden 👌</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-27" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="6b474c72-de6b-44c5-8dee-7452adff25ab" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Toppen! Tack ska du ha!😊</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-28" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="e075ccfb-71ce-48e6-9646-dbda16f1281f" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="69" class="">Så lite! 😊 Det här kommer bli ett riktigt kul och nyttigt projekt 🚀</p>
<p data-start="71" data-end="191" class="">När du fått din API-nyckel, hojta till så kopplar vi ihop den med koden och börjar visa riktiga laddstationer på kartan!</p>
<p data-start="193" data-end="301" class="">Tills dess – om du vill kan jag hjälpa dig ladda upp mock-datan så du får något att visa direkt på hemsidan.</p>
<p data-start="303" data-end="387" class="">Lycka till med ansökan, och bara hör av dig när du är redo att ta nästa steg! ⚡🗺️💻</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-29" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="7d71777f-a221-479a-ab81-d1d1bbd7968c" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Jag fortsätter gärna med att ladda upp för att testa? Kommer jag kunna visuellt se hur utkastet ser ut när det är uppladdat?</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-30" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="13816a6c-e20c-4229-9dea-f5a44f079aee" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="45" class="">Ja absolut – toppen att du vill fortsätta! 🙌</p>
<h3 data-start="47" data-end="111" class="">✅ När du laddat upp projektet (inkl. mock-datan), så kan du:</h3>
<ul data-start="113" data-end="313">
<li data-start="113" data-end="179" class="">
<p data-start="115" data-end="179" class=""><strong data-start="115" data-end="140">Köra projektet lokalt</strong> på din dator (med <code data-start="159" data-end="172">npm run dev</code> t.ex.)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="180" data-end="232" class="">
<p data-start="182" data-end="232" class=""><strong data-start="182" data-end="211">Se utkastet i webbläsaren</strong>, med karta och lista</p>
</li>
<li data-start="233" data-end="277" class="">
<p data-start="235" data-end="277" class=""><strong data-start="235" data-end="260">Filtrera mellan AC/DC</strong> med kryssrutorna</p>
</li>
<li data-start="278" data-end="313" class="">
<p data-start="280" data-end="313" class=""><strong data-start="280" data-end="313">Få upp info i popup på kartan</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="315" data-end="318" class="">
<h2 data-start="320" data-end="357" class="">🚀 Så här laddar du upp och testar</h2>
<h3 data-start="359" data-end="391" class="">1. 📦 Skapa projektet lokalt</h3>
<p data-start="392" data-end="458" class="">Om du inte redan har ett projekt, kan du göra så här i terminalen:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="460" data-end="554"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378