  </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"stations"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"id"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"1"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"name"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Stora Torget Laddstation"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"operator"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"InCharge"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"lat"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">59.3293</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"lng"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">18.0686</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"price"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">3.5</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"type"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"AC"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"power"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">22</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"id"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"2"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"name"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Snabbladdare Malmö"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"operator"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"E.ON"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"lat"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">55.605</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"lng"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">13.0038</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"price"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">4.8</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"type"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"DC"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
      </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"power"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-number">150</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span></span><span>
  </span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="1267" data-end="1349" class="">4. 🧠 Klistra in React-koden du fick i <code data-start="1310" data-end="1331">src/pages/index.jsx</code> (eller <code data-start="1339" data-end="1348">App.jsx</code>)</h3>
<p data-start="1350" data-end="1393" class="">Använd koden du ser i Canvas här i ChatGPT.</p>
<hr data-start="1395" data-end="1398" class="">
<h3 data-start="1400" data-end="1430" class="">🔍 5. Kör lokalt och testa</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="1431" data-end="1454"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378 6.10476 20.3159L8.97693 19.8372C9.72813 19.712 10.1037 19.6494 10.4542 19.521C10.7652 19.407 11.0608 19.2549 11.3343 19.068C11.6425 18.8575 11.9118 18.5882 12.4503 18.0497L20 10.5C21.3807 9.11929 21.3807 6.88071 20 5.5C18.6193 4.11929 16.3807 4.11929 15 5.5L7.45026 13.0497C6.91175 13.5882 6.6425 13.8575 6.43197 14.1657C6.24513 14.4392 6.09299 14.7348 5.97903 15.0458C5.85062 15.3963 5.78802 15.7719 5.66282 16.5231Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M14.5 7L18.5 11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>Redigera</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-bash"><span><span>npm run dev
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1456" data-end="1557" class="">Gå till <code data-start="1464" data-end="1487">http://localhost:5173</code> (eller porten som visas i terminalen) – där ser du kartan och listan!</p>
<hr data-start="1559" data-end="1562" class="">
<p data-start="1564" data-end="1702" class="">Vill du att jag sammanställer allt ovan som en ZIP du kan ladda ner och bara köra direkt i VS Code eller Codesandbox? Det är ännu enklare.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-31" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="ec29560c-bbcb-4d95-b2a8-040cf07a477f" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Ja tack, du får gärna hjälpa mig med det! Men jag trodde att jag skulle ladda upp allt i GitHub och att jag då lokalt inte behövde göra nått på min dator?</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-32" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="d04c53f5-5d2a-4a1e-af96-23ce6fb0eed4" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="70" class="">Grymt! 🎉 Här är en komplett ZIP-fil med ett startklart React-projekt:</p>
<p data-start="72" data-end="145" class="">🔽 <strong data-start="75" data-end="145"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="77" data-end="143" class="cursor-pointer">Ladda ner laddpriskarta.zip</a></span></strong></p>
<hr data-start="147" data-end="150" class="">
<h2 data-start="152" data-end="167" class="">📦 Innehåll:</h2>
<ul data-start="168" data-end="355">
<li data-start="168" data-end="202" class="">
<p data-start="170" data-end="202" class=""><code data-start="170" data-end="190">mock-stations.json</code> i <code data-start="193" data-end="202">public/</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="203" data-end="269" class="">
<p data-start="205" data-end="269" class="">Färdig React-komponent (<code data-start="229" data-end="239">Home.jsx</code>) med karta, popup, filtrering</p>
</li>
<li data-start="270" data-end="355" class="">
<p data-start="272" data-end="355" class="">Du kan anpassa eller flytta till <code data-start="305" data-end="314">App.jsx</code> beroende på hur du organiserar projektet</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="357" data-end="360" class="">
<h2 data-start="362" data-end="381" class="">💡 Så gör du nu:</h2>
<ol data-start="382" data-end="611">
<li data-start="382" data-end="422" class="">
<p data-start="385" data-end="422" class=""><strong data-start="385" data-end="422">Ladda ner och extrahera ZIP-filen</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="423" data-end="469" class="">
<p data-start="426" data-end="469" class="">Öppna mappen i VS Code (eller annan editor)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="470" data-end="533" class="">
<p data-start="473" data-end="533" class="">Se till att ha React och Leaflet installerat (<code data-start="519" data-end="532">npm install</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="534" data-end="561" class="">
<p data-start="537" data-end="561" class="">Starta med <code data-start="548" data-end="561">npm run dev</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="562" data-end="611" class="">
<p data-start="565" data-end="611" class="">Gå till <code data-start="573" data-end="596">http://localhost:5173</code> för att testa!</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="613" data-end="616" class="">
<p data-start="618" data-end="758" class="">Vill du att jag visar hur du pushar detta till ditt GitHub-repo direkt efteråt också? 💪 ​<span class="" data-state="closed"><button><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 19 15" fill="none" class="text-token-link hover:text-token-link-hover ms-0.5 -mt-0.5 inline-block" width="19" height="15"><path d="M4.42 0.75H2.8625H2.75C1.64543 0.75 0.75 1.64543 0.75 2.75V11.65C0.75 12.7546 1.64543 13.65 2.75 13.65H2.8625C2.8625 13.65 2.8625 13.65 2.8625 13.65C2.8625 13.65 4.00751 13.65 4.42 13.65M13.98 13.65H15.5375H15.65C16.7546 13.65 17.65 12.7546 17.65 11.65V2.75C17.65 1.64543 16.7546 0.75 15.65 0.75H15.5375H13.98" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.55283 4.21963C5.25993 3.92674 4.78506 3.92674 4.49217 4.21963C4.19927 4.51252 4.19927 4.9874 4.49217 5.28029L6.36184 7.14996L4.49217 9.01963C4.19927 9.31252 4.19927 9.7874 4.49217 10.0803C4.78506 10.3732 5.25993 10.3732 5.55283 10.0803L7.95283 7.68029C8.24572 7.3874 8.24572 6.91252 7.95283 6.61963L5.55283 4.21963Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M9.77753 8.75003C9.3357 8.75003 8.97753 9.10821 8.97753 9.55003C8.97753 9.99186 9.3357 10.35 9.77753 10.35H13.2775C13.7194 10.35 14.0775 9.99186 14.0775 9.55003C14.0775 9.10821 13.7194 8.75003 13.2775 8.75003H9.77753Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.1"></path></svg></button></span>​</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-33" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem]