</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<blockquote data-start="847" data-end="1050">
<p data-start="849" data-end="1050" class="">💡 Om du får ett fel som kräver inloggning – använd GitHub CLI eller logga in via terminaln med <code data-start="945" data-end="960">gh auth login</code>, eller använd en <strong data-start="978" data-end="1009">personal access token (PAT)</strong> som lösenord (GitHub kräver det numera).</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1052" data-end="1055" class="">
<h2 data-start="1057" data-end="1068" class="">✅ Klart!</h2>
<p data-start="1069" data-end="1236" class="">När du gjort detta kommer projektet att ligga live i ditt repo:<br data-start="1132" data-end="1135">
🔗 <a data-start="1138" data-end="1236" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="" href="https://github.com/Laddpriskollen/laddpriskarta">https://github.com/Laddpriskollen/laddpriskarta</a></p>
<p data-start="1238" data-end="1364" class="">Vill du också att jag guidar hur du deployar det på <strong data-start="1290" data-end="1300">Vercel</strong> eller <strong data-start="1307" data-end="1323">GitHub Pages</strong> så du ser det live i webbläsaren direkt?</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-35" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="16a36934-c2fe-4adb-a856-c358356e6563" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Hej, jag var tvungen att hasighet avsluta senast och hann inte säga hej då eller testa. Skulle ladda ner din zip fil nyss men det gick inte?</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-36" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="20bc695e-3f07-42a4-9138-15d06814127d" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="79" class="">Hej och välkommen tillbaka! 👋 Inga problem alls – kul att du är igång igen! 🙌</p>
<p data-start="81" data-end="258" class="">Det verkar som om länken till ZIP-filen <strong data-start="121" data-end="145">inte längre är aktiv</strong>, men jag fixar snabbt en ny åt dig med exakt samma innehåll: grundprojektet med karta, mock-data och filtrering.</p>
<p data-start="260" data-end="338" class="">✅ Jag genererar en ny <code data-start="282" data-end="301">laddpriskarta.zip</code> åt dig nu – klart om några sekunder…</p></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="908c8353-2b85-45b6-b726-b4b5ac73a9fd" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="135" class="">Här kommer en färsk version av ZIP-filen med hela projektet:<br data-start="60" data-end="63">
📦 <span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="66" data-end="135" class="cursor-pointer">👉 Ladda ner laddpriskarta.zip</a></span></p>
<hr data-start="137" data-end="140" class="">
<h2 data-start="142" data-end="155" class="">✅ Innehåll</h2>
<ul data-start="156" data-end="305">
<li data-start="156" data-end="197" class="">
<p data-start="158" data-end="197" class="">Mock-data (<code data-start="169" data-end="196">public/mock-stations.json</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="198" data-end="260" class="">
<p data-start="200" data-end="260" class="">React-komponent med karta, popup och filtrering (<code data-start="249" data-end="259">Home.jsx</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="261" data-end="305" class="">
<p data-start="263" data-end="305" class="">Redo att användas i ett Vite/React-projekt</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="307" data-end="310" class="">
<p data-start="312" data-end="323" class="">Vill du nu:</p>
<ol data-start="324" data-end="426">
<li data-start="324" data-end="359" class="">
<p data-start="327" data-end="359" class="">Lägga in det i ditt GitHub-repo?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="360" data-end="426" class="">
<p data-start="363" data-end="426" class="">Se det live direkt via t.ex. <strong data-start="392" data-end="402">Vercel</strong> eller <strong data-start="409" data-end="425">GitHub Pages</strong>?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="428" data-end="543" class="">Jag guidar gärna vidare beroende på vilket du vill testa först! ​<span class="" data-state="closed"><button><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 19 15" fill="none" class="text-token-link hover:text-token-link-hover ms-0.5 -mt-0.5 inline-block" width="19" height="15"><path d="M4.42 0.75H2.8625H2.75C1.64543 0.75 0.75 1.64543 0.75 2.75V11.65C0.75 12.7546 1.64543 13.65 2.75 13.65H2.8625C2.8625 13.65 2.8625 13.65 2.8625 13.65C2.8625 13.65 4.00751 13.65 4.42 13.65M13.98 13.65H15.5375H15.65C16.7546 13.65 17.65 12.7546 17.65 11.65V2.75C17.65 1.64543 16.7546 0.75 15.65 0.75H15.5375H13.98" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.55283 4.21963C5.25993 3.92674 4.78506 3.92674 4.49217 4.21963C4.19927 4.51252 4.19927 4.9874 4.49217 5.28029L6.36184 7.14996L4.49217 9.01963C4.19927 9.31252 4.19927 9.7874 4.49217 10.0803C4.78506 10.3732 5.25993 10.3732 5.55283 10.0803L7.95283 7.68029C8.24572 7.3874 8.24572 6.91252 7.95283 6.61963L5.55283 4.21963Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M9.77753 8.75003C9.3357 8.75003 8.97753 9.10821 8.97753 9.55003C8.97753 9.99186 9.3357 10.35 9.77753 10.35H13.2775C13.7194 10.35 14.0775 9.99186 14.0775 9.55003C14.0775 9.10821 13.7194 8.75003 13.2775 8.75003H9.77753Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.1"></path></svg></button></span>​</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-37" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h5 class="sr-only">Du sade:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="aca9dace-df96-4fc9-8273-007463ceda3b" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5"><div class="w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">ja gärna! innan det, behöver jag gå igenom stegen i terminalen som du tidigare nämnde?</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-38" data-scroll-anchor="false"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="c99a4824-fe29-4e93-9b94-5cd210c68552" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="172" class="">Ja! För att ladda upp projektet till <strong data-start="37" data-end="53">GitHub-repot</strong> du redan har skapat, behöver du gå igenom några enkla terminalsteg <strong data-start="121" data-end="132">en gång</strong>. Här är allt du behöver i rätt ordning:</p>
<hr data-start="174" data-end="177" class="">
<h2 data-start="179" data-end="236" class="">🚀 Steg-för-steg: Ladda upp ZIP-innehållet till GitHub</h2>
<h3 data-start="238" data-end="271" class="">🧩 <strong data-start="245" data-end="271">1. Extrahera ZIP-filen</strong></h3>
<p data-start="272" data-end="326" class="">Packa upp <code data-start="282" data-end="301">laddpriskarta.zip</code> någonstans på din dator.</p>
<h3 data-start="328" data-end="379" class="">🔧 <strong data-start="335" data-end="379">2. Öppna terminal i den uppackade mappen</strong></h3>
<p data-start="380" data-end="417" class="">Gå till mappen i din terminal, t.ex.:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="419" data-end="460"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378