  </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"dev"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"vite"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"build"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"vite build"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
  </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"preview"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"vite preview"</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<blockquote data-start="657" data-end="726">
<p data-start="659" data-end="726" class="">Om den inte finns, skapa en <code data-start="687" data-end="701">package.json</code> med <code data-start="706" data-end="719">npm init -y</code> först.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="728" data-end="731" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="733" data-end="756" class="">💾 När det är gjort:</h2>
<h3 data-start="758" data-end="796" class="">4. Commit &amp; push till GitHub igen:</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="798" data-end="907"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378