67 19.7071 4.2929C21.4784 6.06414 21.4784 8.93588 19.7071 10.7071L18.7073 11.7069L11.6135 18.8007C10.8766 19.5376 9.92793 20.0258 8.89999 20.1971L4.16441 20.9864C3.84585 21.0395 3.52127 20.9355 3.29291 20.7071C3.06454 20.4788 2.96053 20.1542 3.01362 19.8356L3.80288 15.1C3.9742 14.0721 4.46243 13.1234 5.19932 12.3865L13.2929 4.29291ZM13 7.41422L6.61353 13.8007C6.1714 14.2428 5.87846 14.8121 5.77567 15.4288L5.21656 18.7835L8.57119 18.2244C9.18795 18.1216 9.75719 17.8286 10.1993 17.3865L16.5858 11L13 7.41422ZM18 9.5858L14.4142 6.00001L14.7071 5.70712C15.6973 4.71693 17.3027 4.71693 18.2929 5.70712C19.2831 6.69731 19.2831 8.30272 18.2929 9.29291L18 9.5858Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-56" data-scroll-anchor="false" style=""><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="c1311813-cc71-42b1-9047-edd1ca0f18d1" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="273" class="">Tack för att du delade hela felkatalogen från Vercel! Det där är deras officiella lista över <strong data-start="93" data-end="113">möjliga felkoder</strong> som kan uppstå under en deploy – men <strong data-start="151" data-end="200">om din sida fungerar och deployen gick igenom</strong>, så behöver du <strong data-start="216" data-end="240">inte göra något alls</strong> med den informationen just nu 🙌</p>
<hr data-start="275" data-end="278" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="280" data-end="306" class="">✅ Är allt okej just nu?</h2>
<p data-start="308" data-end="314" class="">Om du:</p>
<ul data-start="315" data-end="476">
<li data-start="315" data-end="392" class="" style="">
<p data-start="317" data-end="392" class="">Har en <strong data-start="324" data-end="337">live-länk</strong> från Vercel (t.ex. <code data-start="357" data-end="391">https://laddpriskarta.vercel.app</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="393" data-end="444" class="" style="">
<p data-start="395" data-end="444" class="">Ser din karta och lista med mockade laddstationer</p>
</li>
<li data-start="445" data-end="476" class="" style="">
<p data-start="447" data-end="476" class="">Kan bocka i/ur AC &amp; DC-filter</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="478" data-end="527" class="">…då är vi <strong data-start="488" data-end="502">helt hemma</strong> för första versionen! 🥳</p>
<hr data-start="529" data-end="532" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="534" data-end="559" class="">Nästa förslag på steg:</h2>
<p data-start="560" data-end="605" class="">Vill du att vi går vidare med någon av dessa?</p>
<ol data-start="607" data-end="935">
<li data-start="607" data-end="658" class="" style="">
<p data-start="610" data-end="658" class="">🔌 <strong data-start="613" data-end="636">Koppla in NOBIL API</strong> istället för mockdata</p>
</li>
<li data-start="659" data-end="710" class="" style="">
<p data-start="662" data-end="710" class="">🎨 <strong data-start="665" data-end="701">Visa operatörens färg eller ikon</strong> i kartan</p>
</li>
<li data-start="711" data-end="762" class="" style="">
<p data-start="714" data-end="762" class="">📱 <strong data-start="717" data-end="737">Responsiv design</strong> för mobil och surfplatta</p>
</li>
<li data-start="763" data-end="827" class="" style="">
<p data-start="766" data-end="827" class="">🔍 <strong data-start="769" data-end="827">Filtrera på lägsta pris, högsta effekt, tillgänglighet</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="828" data-end="874" class="" style="">
<p data-start="831" data-end="874" class="">📝 Skapa snygg <strong data-start="846" data-end="859">README.md</strong> till ditt repo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="875" data-end="935" class="" style="">
<p data-start="878" data-end="935" class="">⚙️ Lägga in .env-fil så du kan hantera API-nycklar säkert</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="937" data-end="993" class="">Bara välj vad du vill göra härnäst, så kör vi vidare! 💪</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex absolute start-0 end-0 flex justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex items-center p-1 select-none -mt-1 focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none duration-500 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-position:100%_0%] [mask-size:300%_100%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Kopiera" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button"><span class="touch:w-[38px] flex h-[30px] w-[30px] items-center justify-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bra svar" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button"><span class="touch:w-[38px] flex h-[30px] w-[30px] ite