stify-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-58" data-scroll-anchor="false" style=""><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="96624cf3-a00f-4fe0-8cce-1ac87c60b59f" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="71" class="">Ja, jag ser skärmdumpen – tack!<br data-start="31" data-end="34">
Det visar en klassisk Vercel-felsida:</p>
<blockquote data-start="73" data-end="151">
<p data-start="75" data-end="151" class=""><strong data-start="75" data-end="93">404: NOT_FOUND</strong><br data-start="93" data-end="96">
Det betyder att <strong data-start="114" data-end="150">startsidan (index) inte hittades</strong>.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="153" data-end="156" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="158" data-end="185" class="">🛠️ Varför händer detta?</h2>
<p data-start="186" data-end="382" class="">Du använder troligen en mappstruktur där din huvudsida ligger i <code data-start="250" data-end="270">src/pages/Home.jsx</code>, men <strong data-start="276" data-end="348">Vercel förväntar sig en <code data-start="302" data-end="314">index.html</code> eller <code data-start="321" data-end="332">index.jsx</code> i root-mappen</strong> – eller att den byggs med <code data-start="375" data-end="381">vite</code>.</p>
<hr data-start="384" data-end="387" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="389" data-end="455" class="">✅ Lösning A – Flytta <code data-start="413" data-end="423">Home.jsx</code> till <code data-start="429" data-end="438">App.jsx</code> eller <code data-start="445" data-end="455">main.jsx</code></h2>
<p data-start="457" data-end="477" class="">Det enklaste är att:</p>
<ol data-start="478" data-end="609">
<li data-start="478" data-end="533" class="" style="">
<p data-start="481" data-end="533" class=""><strong data-start="481" data-end="533">Flytta innehållet från <code data-start="506" data-end="516">Home.jsx</code> till <code data-start="522" data-end="531">App.jsx</code></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="534" data-end="609" class="" style="">
<p data-start="537" data-end="609" class="">Se till att projektet använder en vanlig <code data-start="578" data-end="588">main.jsx</code> + <code data-start="591" data-end="600">App.jsx</code>-struktur</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="611" data-end="743" class="">Vill du att jag ger dig en komplett, fungerande <code data-start="659" data-end="668">App.jsx</code>, <code data-start="670" data-end="680">main.jsx</code> och uppdaterad <code data-start="696" data-end="708">index.html</code> så det fungerar direkt med Vercel?</p>
<hr data-start="745" data-end="748" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="750" data-end="784" class="">✅ Alternativ B – Använd routing</h2>
<p data-start="786" data-end="961" class="">Om du vill behålla <code data-start="805" data-end="815">Home.jsx</code>, då behöver du använda en router (som React Router) och konfigurera <code data-start="884" data-end="887">/</code>-routen. Men för en enkel sida rekommenderar jag <strong data-start="936" data-end="952">alternativ A</strong> just nu.</p>
<hr data-start="963" data-end="966" class="" style="">
<p data-start="968" data-end="1056" class="">Vill du att jag packar en fungerande version med rätt struktur åt dig direkt som ZIP? 😄</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex absolute start-0 end-0 flex justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex items-center p-1 select-none -mt-1 focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none duration-500 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-position:100%_0%] [mask-size:300%_100%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Kopiera" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button"><span class="touch:w-[38px] flex h-[30px] w-[30px] items-center justify-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bra svar" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button"><span class="touch:w-