<p data-start="72" data-end="157" class="">📦 <strong data-start="75" data-end="157"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="77" data-end="155" class="cursor-pointer">Ladda ner laddpriskarta_fixed.zip</a></span></strong></p>
<hr data-start="159" data-end="162" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="164" data-end="186" class="">✅ Vad som är fixat:</h2>
<ul data-start="187" data-end="390">
<li data-start="187" data-end="222" class="" style="">
<p data-start="189" data-end="222" class=""><code data-start="189" data-end="198">App.jsx</code> innehåller hela kartvyn</p>
</li>
<li data-start="223" data-end="260" class="" style="">
<p data-start="225" data-end="260" class=""><code data-start="225" data-end="235">main.jsx</code> sätter upp React korrekt</p>
</li>
<li data-start="261" data-end="307" class="" style="">
<p data-start="263" data-end="307" class=""><code data-start="263" data-end="275">index.html</code> finns i root, som Vercel kräver</p>
</li>
<li data-start="308" data-end="350" class="" style="">
<p data-start="310" data-end="350" class=""><code data-start="310" data-end="316">vite</code> finns definierat i <code data-start="336" data-end="350">package.json</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="351" data-end="390" class="" style="">
<p data-start="353" data-end="390" class="">Inkluderar mock-stationer och styling</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="392" data-end="395" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="397" data-end="414" class="">🚀 Nästa steg:</h2>
<ol data-start="416" data-end="512">
<li data-start="416" data-end="439" class="" style="">
<p data-start="419" data-end="439" class=""><strong data-start="419" data-end="439">Packa upp ZIP:en</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="440" data-end="504" class="" style="">
<p data-start="443" data-end="504" class="">Byt ut innehållet i ditt befintliga repo (ersätt gamla filer)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="505" data-end="512" class="" style="">
<p data-start="508" data-end="512" class="">Kör:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="514" data-end="610"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378