" height="1256" class="max-w-full object-cover object-center overflow-hidden rounded-lg w-full h-full max-w-96 max-h-64 w-fit transition-opacity duration-300 opacity-100" src="./marker-icon_files/file-2o8sqcJW1pCjktWFbx6teJ"></button></div></div></div></div><div class="relative max-w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] bg-token-message-surface rounded-3xl px-5 py-2.5 rounded-se-lg"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">Behöver jag göra nått mer? Fel verkar kvarstå, se skärmdump </div></div></div></div></div><div class="text-token-text-secondary my-2 me-4 flex flex-row justify-end gap-1 text-xs"></div></div><div class="flex absolute start-0 end-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex items-center p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Kopiera" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button"><span class="touch:w-[38px] flex h-[30px] w-[30px] items-center justify-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-62" data-scroll-anchor="false" style=""><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="e33997be-14e9-4c53-8c1b-c4111bf869a4" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="183" class="">Tack för att du delar skärmdumpen – jag ser att <strong data-start="48" data-end="85">404-felet fortfarande ligger kvar</strong>, vilket betyder att Vercel <strong data-start="113" data-end="154">inte hittar startsidan (<code data-start="139" data-end="151">index.html</code>)</strong> i rätt mapp <strong data-start="167" data-end="182">efter build</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="185" data-end="228" class="">Men oroa dig inte – vi löser detta direkt ✅</p>
<hr data-start="230" data-end="233" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="235" data-end="265" class="">🔍 Kontrollera detta först:</h2>
<h3 data-start="267" data-end="316" class="">1. <strong data-start="274" data-end="316">Använder du Vite som framework preset?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="317" data-end="384" class="">När du deployade på Vercel – <strong data-start="346" data-end="383">valde du "Framework Preset: Vite"</strong>?</p>
<p data-start="386" data-end="460" class="">Om du valde “Other”/”Open”, behöver du manuellt ställa in rätt build-path.</p>
<hr data-start="462" data-end="465" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="467" data-end="492" class="">✅ Så här fixar du det:</h2>
<h3 data-start="494" data-end="568" class="">💡 <strong data-start="501" data-end="530">Lösning A (Rekommenderas)</strong>: Ändra projektinställningar på Vercel</h3>
<ol data-start="570" data-end="764">
<li data-start="570" data-end="641" class="" style="">
<p data-start="573" data-end="641" class="">Gå till <a data-start="581" data-end="641" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="">https://vercel.com/dashboard</a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="642" data-end="685" class="" style="">
<p data-start="645" data-end="685" class="">Klicka på ditt projekt (<code data-start="669" data-end="684">laddpriskarta</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="686" data-end="716" class="" style="">
<p data-start="689" data-end="716" class="">Gå till fliken <strong data-start="704" data-end="716">Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="717" data-end="764" class="" style="">
<p data-start="720" data-end="764" class="">Scrolla ner till <strong data-start="737" data-end="764">Build &amp; Output Settings</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="766" data-end="781" class="">Ändra följande:</p>
<div class="group pointer-events-none relative flex justify-center *:pointer-events-auto"><span class="pointer-events-none absolute start-full top-4 z-10 hidden h-full w-fit ps-2 md:block" data-state="closed"><button class="hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary text-token-text-secondary pointer-events-auto rounded-lg px-1 py-1 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></button></span><div class="tableContainer horzScrollShadows relative"><table class="min-w-full" data-start="783" data-end="985"><thead data-start="783" data-end="820"><tr data-start="783" data-end="820"><th data-start="783" data-end="802">Inställning</th><th data-start="802" data-end="820">Värde</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="859" data-end="985"><tr data-start="859" data-end="901"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="859" data-end="882"><strong data-start="861" data-end="881">Framework Preset</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="882" data-end="901"><code data-start="884" data-end="890">Vite</code></td></tr><tr data-start="902" data-end="943"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="902" data-end="924"><strong data-start="904" data-end="921">Build Command</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="924" data-end="943"><code data-start="926" data-end="938">vite build</code></td></tr><tr data-start="944" data-end="985"><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="944" data-end="966"><strong data-start="946" data-end="966">Output Directory</strong></td><td class="max-w-[calc(var(--thread-content-max-width)*2/3)]" data-start="966" data-end="985"><code data-start="968" data-end="974">dist</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
<p data-start="987" data-end="1002" class="">Tryck <strong data-start="993" data-end="1001">Save</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1004" data-end="1007" class="" style="">
<h3 data-start="1009" data-end="1035" class="">🔁 5. Kör om deployen:</h3>
<p data-start="1037" data-end="1129" class="">Gå till <strong data-start="1045" data-end="1063">Deploys-fliken</strong> och klicka på “Redeploy” → då kommer den nya inställningen gälla.</p>
<hr data-start="1131" data-end="1134" class="" style="">
<p data-start="1136" data-end="1279" class="">Vill du att jag sammanställer en guide för hur du kan se <code data-start="1193" data-end="1210">dist/index.html</code> efter build lokalt också, så du kan felsöka offline innan du pushar?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex absolute start-0 end-0 flex justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex items-center p-1 select-none -mt-1 focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none duration-500 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-position:100%_0%] [mask-size:300%_100%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Kopiera" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button"><span class="touch:w-[38px] flex h-[30px] w-[30px] items-center justify-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary 