e-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Kopiera" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button"><span class="touch:w-[38px] flex h-[30px] w-[30px] items-center justify-center"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-md-heavy"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-64" data-scroll-anchor="false" style=""><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT sade:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[70rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(12)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto flex max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="29186c6c-43cb-4fc6-a31f-cd7c1810ef5d" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="187" class="">Tack för skärmdumpen – du har ställt in <strong data-start="40" data-end="65">rätt framework (Vite)</strong> och det ser perfekt ut! ✅<br data-start="91" data-end="94">
Det som återstår nu är att <strong data-start="121" data-end="144">trigga en ny deploy</strong> så Vercel använder dina nya inställningar.</p>
<hr data-start="189" data-end="192" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="194" data-end="236" class="">✅ Så här hittar du <strong data-start="216" data-end="236">Redeploy-knappen</strong></h2>
<ol data-start="238" data-end="400">
<li data-start="238" data-end="309" class="" style="">
<p data-start="241" data-end="309" class="">Gå till <a data-start="249" data-end="309" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="">https://vercel.com/dashboard</a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="310" data-end="351" class="" style="">
<p data-start="313" data-end="351" class="">Klicka på ditt projekt <code data-start="336" data-end="351">laddpriskarta</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="352" data-end="400" class="" style="">
<p data-start="355" data-end="400" class="">Gå till fliken <strong data-start="370" data-end="385">Deployments</strong> (uppe i menyn)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="402" data-end="501" class="">Där ser du senaste deployment (den som gav 404).<br data-start="450" data-end="453">
🟢 Klicka på den, och inne i vyn finns en knapp:</p>
<blockquote data-start="502" data-end="554">
<p data-start="504" data-end="554" class=""><strong data-start="504" data-end="518">“Redeploy”</strong> eller <strong data-start="525" data-end="536">“Retry”</strong> (uppe till höger)</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="556" data-end="559" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="561" data-end="609" class="">Alternativ: Gör en liten kodändring och pusha</h2>
<p data-start="610" data-end="652" class="">Om du inte hittar knappen kan du istället:</p>
<ol data-start="654" data-end="738">
<li data-start="654" data-end="712" class="" style="">
<p data-start="657" data-end="712" class="">Ändra t.ex. en rad i <code data-start="678" data-end="687">App.jsx</code> (lägg till en kommentar)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="713" data-end="738" class="" style="">
<p data-start="716" data-end="738" class="">Spara → commit → push:</p>
</li>
</ol>
