Error: Command "vite build" exited with 127
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="202" data-end="221" class="">💡 Det betyder:</h3>
<p data-start="222" data-end="322" class=""><code data-start="222" data-end="228">vite</code> är <strong data-start="232" data-end="267">inte installerat som dependency</strong> i ditt projekt – så Vercel kan inte köra <code data-start="309" data-end="321">vite build</code>.</p>
<hr data-start="324" data-end="327" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="329" data-end="361" class="">✅ Så här löser du det direkt:</h2>
<h3 data-start="363" data-end="400" class="">1. Gå till projektmappen lokalt</h3>
<p data-start="401" data-end="453" class="">Öppna terminalen i mappen där du har <code data-start="438" data-end="452">package.json</code>.</p>
