</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<blockquote data-start="523" data-end="584">
<p data-start="525" data-end="584" class="">Det lägger till Vite som <strong data-start="550" data-end="567">devDependency</strong> i <code data-start="570" data-end="584">package.json</code></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="586" data-end="589" class="" style="">
