  </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"vite"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"^4.x.x"</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="559" data-end="581" class="">Om det finns – toppen!</p>
<hr data-start="583" data-end="586" class="" style="">
<h3 data-start="588" data-end="614" class="">2. <strong data-start="595" data-end="614">Pusha ändringen</strong></h3>
<p data-start="615" data-end="645" class="">I terminalen, kör nu följande:</p>
