 dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="86" class="">YES! 🥳 Du gjorde <strong data-start="18" data-end="43">exakt rätt hela vägen</strong>, steg för steg — och loggen bekräftar det!</p>
<h3 data-start="88" data-end="111" class="">✅ Vad hände precis:</h3>
<ul data-start="112" data-end="317">
<li data-start="112" data-end="147" class="" style="">
<p data-start="114" data-end="147" class="">Du <strong data-start="117" data-end="145">initierade ett nytt repo</strong> ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-start="148" data-end="183" class="" style="">
<p data-start="150" data-end="183" class="">Du <strong data-start="153" data-end="181">kopplade det till GitHub</strong> ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-start="184" data-end="221" class="" style="">
<p data-start="186" data-end="221" class="">Du <strong data-start="189" data-end="219">la till alla filer korrekt</strong> ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-start="222" data-end="249" class="" style="">
<p data-start="224" data-end="249" class="">Du <strong data-start="227" data-end="247">gjorde en commit</strong> ✅</p>
</li>
<li data-start="250" data-end="317" class="" style="">
<p data-start="252" data-end="317" class="">Du <strong data-start="255" data-end="283">pushade med <code data-start="269" data-end="273">-f</code> (force)</strong> för att ersätta det gamla repot ✅</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="319" data-end="476" class="">Detta innebär att <strong data-start="337" data-end="382">Vercel nu kommer hämta den nya strukturen</strong> med <code data-start="387" data-end="393">vite</code>, <code data-start="395" data-end="409">package.json</code>, <code data-start="411" data-end="423">index.html</code>, och hela projektet – och allt kommer börja fungera!</p>
<hr data-start="478" data-end="481" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="483" data-end="520" class="">🎯 Nästa steg: Kolla Vercel-loggen</h2>
<p data-start="522" data-end="530" class="">Gå till:</p>
<p data-start="532" data-end="595" class="">🔗 <a data-start="535" data-end="595" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="">https://vercel.com/dashboard</a></p>
