<p data-start="600" data-end="639" class="">Klicka på ditt projekt: <code data-start="624" data-end="639">laddpriskarta</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="640" data-end="673" class="" style="">
<p data-start="643" data-end="673" class="">Gå till fliken <strong data-start="658" data-end="673">Deployments</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="674" data-end="728" class="" style="">
<p data-start="677" data-end="728" class="">Välj den senaste deployen (ska ha dagens klockslag)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="729" data-end="847" class="" style="">
