dist/assets/index-xxxxx.js
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="937" data-end="996" class="">Så det borde fungera... <strong data-start="961" data-end="996">om Vercel använder rätt output.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="998" data-end="1001" class="" style="">
<h3 data-start="1003" data-end="1047" class="">3. Möjlig orsak: saknad <code data-start="1031" data-end="1047">vite.config.js</code></h3>
<p data-start="1049" data-end="1197" class="">🧨 Det kan vara att vi <strong data-start="1072" data-end="1106">saknar en <code data-start="1084" data-end="1100">vite.config.js</code>-fil</strong> som säger åt Vite hur root och publicDir ser ut. Då fungerar det lokalt men inte i deploy.</p>
<hr data-start="1199" data-end="1202" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="1204" data-end="1254" class="">💡 Lösning: Lägg till en enkel <code data-start="1238" data-end="1254">vite.config.js</code></h2>
<p data-start="1256" data-end="1335" class="">Vi fixar detta! Jag skapar direkt en korrekt fil du kan lägga till och pusha 👇</p></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="b4ab0270-8b73-476c-a517-4cd56477f871" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="59" class="">Här är din <code data-start="11" data-end="27">vite.config.js</code> som kan lösa det vita fönstret:</p>
<p data-start="61" data-end="128" class="">📄 <strong data-start="64" data-end="128"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="66" data-end="126" class="cursor-pointer">Ladda ner vite.config.js</a></span></strong></p>
<hr data-start="130" data-end="133" class="">
<h2 data-start="135" data-end="151" class="">✅ Gör så här:</h2>
<ol data-start="153" data-end="289">
<li data-start="153" data-end="247" class="">
<p data-start="156" data-end="247" class="">Lägg filen i <strong data-start="169" data-end="198">rotmappen av ditt projekt</strong> (<code data-start="200" data-end="246">C:\Users\danie\Downloads\laddpriskarta_fixed</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="248" data-end="289" class="">
<p data-start="251" data-end="289" class="">Öppna terminalen i den mappen och kör:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="291" data-end="400"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378