pty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="133" class="">Tack för att du klistrar in loggen från <strong data-start="40" data-end="66">konsolen i webbläsaren</strong>! 🙌<br data-start="70" data-end="73">
Jag har granskat det du ser — och det finns <strong data-start="117" data-end="132">bra nyheter</strong>:</p>
<hr data-start="135" data-end="138" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="140" data-end="185" class="">✅ Det är <strong data-start="152" data-end="183">inte ditt fel eller din kod</strong></h2>
<p data-start="186" data-end="274" class="">Alla felmeddelanden du ser gäller <strong data-start="220" data-end="242">Vercels adminpanel</strong>, inte din applikation. Exempel:</p>
<ul data-start="276" data-end="431">
<li data-start="276" data-end="341" class="" style="">
<p data-start="278" data-end="341" class=""><code data-start="278" data-end="341">Failed to load resource: ... team is not allowed to block IPs</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="342" data-end="363" class="" style="">
<p data-start="344" data-end="363" class=""><code data-start="344" data-end="363">Unauthorized: ...</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="364" data-end="403" class="" style="">
<p data-start="366" data-end="403" class=""><code data-start="366" data-end="403">Deprecated API for given entry type</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="404" data-end="431" class="" style="">
<p data-start="406" data-end="431" class=""><code data-start="406" data-end="421">status of 504</code> för <code data-start="426" data-end="431">jwt</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="433" data-end="457" class="">🔍 Dessa handlar om:</h3>
<ul data-start="458" data-end="632">
<li data-start="458" data-end="507" class="" style="">
<p data-start="460" data-end="507" class="">Interna fetch-anrop i <strong data-start="482" data-end="507">Vercels kontrollpanel</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="508" data-end="551" class="" style="">
<p data-start="510" data-end="551" class="">Inget som påverkar din <strong data-start="533" data-end="551">egen React-app</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="552" data-end="632" class="" style="">
<p data-start="554" data-end="632" class="">Du ser dem bara om du har devtools öppet på <code data-start="598" data-end="610">vercel.app</code>, inte på din webbsida</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="634" data-end="637" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="639" data-end="693" class="">🤔 Men varför är din <strong data-start="663" data-end="692">egen sida fortfarande vit</strong>?</h2>
<p data-start="695" data-end="819" class="">Om konsolen inte visar <strong data-start="718" data-end="744">något fel från din kod</strong> (t.ex. <code data-start="752" data-end="762">main.jsx</code>, <code data-start="764" data-end="773">App.jsx</code>, eller <code data-start="781" data-end="787">vite</code>), så är nästa troligaste orsak:</p>
<blockquote data-start="821" data-end="887">
<p data-start="823" data-end="887" class=""><strong data-start="823" data-end="861">CSS eller layout döljer innehållet</strong>, eller kartan har 0 höjd.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="889" data-end="892" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="894" data-end="940" class="">✅ Test: Lägg till bakgrundsfärg i <code data-start="931" data-end="940">App.jsx</code></h2>
<p data-start="942" data-end="1008" class="">För att se om något visas, öppna <code data-start="975" data-end="990">src/index.css</code> och ändra så här:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="1010" data-end="1092"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">css</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.37