-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="96" class="">Toppen! Här är uppdaterade projektet med visuella justeringar så du ser något direkt på skärmen:</p>
<p data-start="98" data-end="205" class="">🎨 <strong data-start="101" data-end="205"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="103" data-end="203" class="cursor-pointer">Ladda ner laddpriskarta_fixed_visual_fix.zip</a></span></strong></p>
<hr data-start="207" data-end="210" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="212" data-end="237" class="">✅ Detta har jag fixat:</h2>
<ul data-start="238" data-end="465">
<li data-start="238" data-end="287" class="" style="">
<p data-start="240" data-end="287" class="">🔹 Ljusgrå bakgrund i hela layouten (<code data-start="277" data-end="286">#f2f2f2</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="288" data-end="331" class="" style="">
<p data-start="290" data-end="331" class="">🔹 <code data-start="293" data-end="304">index.css</code> med bakgrundsfärg och font</p>
</li>
<li data-start="332" data-end="415" class="" style="">
<p data-start="334" data-end="415" class="">🔹 Inline-style i <code data-start="352" data-end="361">App.jsx</code> så att något alltid syns – även om kartan inte laddas</p>
</li>
<li data-start="416" data-end="465" class="" style="">
<p data-start="418" data-end="465" class="">💡 Användbart för felsökning och layoutkontroll</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="467" data-end="470" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="472" data-end="486" class="">Nästa steg:</h2>
<ol data-start="487" data-end="586">
<li data-start="487" data-end="506" class="" style="">
<p data-start="490" data-end="506" class="">Packa upp ZIP:en</p>
</li>
<li data-start="507" data-end="578" class="" style="">
<p data-start="510" data-end="578" class="">Kopiera över innehållet till din projektmapp (<code data-start="556" data-end="577">laddpriskarta_fixed</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="579" data-end="586" class="" style="">
<p data-start="582" data-end="586" class="">Kör:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="588" data-end="687"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378