<hr data-start="47" data-end="50" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="52" data-end="87" class="">✅ Ja, <strong data-start="61" data-end="87">du ska ersätta filerna</strong></h2>
<p data-start="88" data-end="141" class="">De två filerna det gäller är med största sannolikhet:</p>
<ol data-start="143" data-end="178">
<li data-start="143" data-end="159" class="" style="">
<p data-start="146" data-end="159" class=""><code data-start="146" data-end="159">src/App.jsx</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="160" data-end="178" class="" style="">
<p data-start="163" data-end="178" class=""><code data-start="163" data-end="178">src/index.css</code></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="180" data-end="202" class="">De är uppdaterade med:</p>
<ul data-start="203" data-end="274">
<li data-start="203" data-end="218" class="" style="">
<p data-start="205" data-end="218" class="">Bakgrundsfärg</p>
</li>
<li data-start="219" data-end="231" class="" style="">
<p data-start="221" data-end="231" class="">Layout-fix</p>
</li>
<li data-start="232" data-end="274" class="" style="">
<p data-start="234" data-end="274" class="">Visuellt innehåll så du slipper vit sida</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="276" data-end="279" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="281" data-end="297" class="">💡 Så gör du:</h2>
<p data-start="298" data-end="348" class="">När du får meddelandet om att filerna redan finns:</p>
<p data-start="350" data-end="427" class="">👉 Välj <strong data-start="358" data-end="386">"Ersätt filerna i målet"</strong> (eller motsvarande på svenska i Windows)</p>
<hr data-start="429" data-end="432" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="434" data-end="450" class="">🟢 Efter det:</h2>
<ol data-start="451" data-end="500">
<li data-start="451" data-end="492" class="" style="">
<p data-start="454" data-end="492" class="">Öppna terminal i <code data-start="471" data-end="492">laddpriskarta_fixed</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="493" data-end="500" class="" style="">
<p data-start="496" data-end="500" class="">Kör:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="501" data-end="611"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-md border-[0.5px] border-token-border-medium relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary select-none rounded-t-[5px]">bash</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary text-token-text-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary flex items-center rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none px-4 py-1" aria-label="Kopiera"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7 5C7 3.34315 8.34315 2 10 2H19C20.6569 2 22 3.34315 22 5V14C22 15.6569 20.6569 17 19 17H17V19C17 20.6569 15.6569 22 14 22H5C3.34315 22 2 20.6569 2 19V10C2 8.34315 3.34315 7 5 7H7V5ZM9 7H14C15.6569 7 17 8.34315 17 10V15H19C19.5523 15 20 14.5523 20 14V5C20 4.44772 19.5523 4 19 4H10C9.44772 4 9 4.44772 9 5V7ZM5 9C4.44772 9 4 9.44772 4 10V19C4 19.5523 4.44772 20 5 20H14C14.5523 20 15 19.5523 15 19V10C15 9.44772 14.5523 9 14 9H5Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg>Kopiera</button></span><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="flex items-center gap-1 px-4 py-1 select-none"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-xs"><path d="M2.5 5.5C4.3 5.2 5.2 4 5.5 2.5C5.8 4 6.7 5.2 8.5 5.5C6.7 5.8 5.8 7 5.5 8.5C5.2 7 4.3 5.8 2.5 5.5Z" fill="currentColor" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.66282 16.5231L5.18413 19.3952C5.12203 19.7678 5.09098 19.9541 5.14876 20.0888C5.19933 20.2067 5.29328 20.3007 5.41118 20.3512C5.54589 20.409 5.73218 20.378