mpty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light"><p data-start="0" data-end="156" class="">Ah, jag är tillfälligt offline från internet så jag kan inte hämta bilderna direkt åt dig – men <strong data-start="96" data-end="153">jag har en enkel lösning du kan göra själv nu direkt!</strong> 👇</p>
<hr data-start="158" data-end="161" class="" style="">
<h2 data-start="163" data-end="209" class="">🛠️ Så fixar du Leaflet-markörerna manuellt</h2>
<h3 data-start="211" data-end="257" class="">1. Ladda ner dessa 3 filer till din dator:</h3>
<ul data-start="259" data-end="520">
<li data-start="259" data-end="342" class="" style="">
<p data-start="261" data-end="342" class="">🔗 <a data-start="264" data-end="342" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="">marker-icon.png</a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="343" data-end="432" class="" style="">
<p data-start="345" data-end="432" class="">🔗 <a data-start="348" data-end="432" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="">marker-icon-2x.png</a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="433" data-end="520" class="">
<p data-start="435" data-end="520" class="">🔗 <a data-start="438" data-end="520" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="">marker-shadow.png</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote data-start="522" data-end="583">
<p data-start="524" data-end="583" class="">Högerklicka → "Spara som…"<br data-start="550" data-end="553">
Lägg dem t.ex. i <code data-start="572" data-end="583">Downloads</code></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="585" data-end="588" class="">
